data.description: Welcome home to a mid century ranch in Royal Manor subdivision. Open floor plan for your convenience  Spacious great room, 3 generous size bedrooms, full bath, laundry room, kitchen with stove, oven,dishwasher,refrigerator,microwave,garbage disposal new in 2021, lots of cabinets, ample eat space and bonus room for a home office etc. Nice covered patio in rear overlooking a large back yard. 1 car garage with opener. New roof in 2021, new flooring thur out except bedrooms in 2022. Very close to Gahanna schools,shopping and parks. Easy accessto 270, 670 to downtown, Airport,Easton and Intel.
